<h1 style="text-align:center; color:#000066">
Why God Loves Us<br>And How We can Love Others
</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;">
By <a href="brandon.html">Rev. Brandon A. Olivares</a><br>
Johnstown, PA, USA
</p>

<div style="float:left; margin:2px 6px 6px 0px;">
<script type="text/javascript"><!--
google_ad_client = "pub-7242869414180671";
